{"tid":1944452,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"觀塘糖水鋪老闆娘好好人，要幫襯佢","createTime":"2020-03-26T11:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T11:41:35.000Z","uid":126560,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c94cb21bf26461cfb05250f7b2a39ec29634c018","tid":1944452,"uid":126560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:33:16.000Z","msg":"今日同女友去食糖水，賣完單行出門口幾步先驚覺自己冇載口罩，以為漏左係鋪，即刻返去間鋪，老闆娘話冇見過，之後話俾個我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔好意思咁拎完講聲多謝走左，事後先揾到個口罩原來係褲袋俾電話壓住左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，以後會多啲幫襯佢，啲芋圓同燉蛋好好食。(係宜安街)"},{"pid":"b514aff3e26a2176007022943b7f074688eddf19","tid":1944452,"uid":52793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:41:13.000Z","msg":"仲出去食糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9b02c37faf07c101fa2fd516b8c115e19a05bd","tid":1944452,"uid":201414,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T11:41:35.000Z","msg":"屌你老母死打手 好人就吹雞叫人幫襯？！咁黃店呢 當黃店汁曬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}